text: Obed Mfanyana Dlamini (4 April 1937 - 18 January 2017) was a Swazi politician. He served as Prime Minister of Swaziland from 12 July 1989 to 25 October 1993. He was born in Mhlosheni. Dlamini died from an illness on 18 January 2017 in Johannesburg, South Africa.
